     1 IDENTIFICATION  DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EXERC2.
     3 AUTHOR.         YHAGO PESSOA.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   26/02/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 17:48.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8*REMARKS.  LE OS REGISTRO DO ARQUIVO DE ENTRADA
     9*          CADALU(CODIGO, NOME, SEXO, DATA) E GRAVA NO
    10*          ARQUIVO DE SAIDA CADATU(CODIGO, NOME, DATA).
    11
    12 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    13 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    14 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    15 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    16 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    17
    18 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    19 FILE-CONTROL.
    20     SELECT   CADALU      ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    21     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    22     SELECT   CADATU        ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    23     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    24
    25 DATA           DIVISION.
    26 FILE SECTION.
    27
    28 FD  CADALU
    29     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    30     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS          "CADALU.DAT".
    31 01  REG-ENT.
    32     02 NUM-ENT           PIC 9(05).
    33     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    34     02 SEXO-ENT          PIC X(01).
    35     02 DD-ENT            PIC 9(02).
    36     02 MM-ENT            PIC 9(02).
    37     02 AAAA-ENT          PIC 9(04).
    38
    39 FD  CADATU
    40     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    41     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CADATU.DAT".
    42 01  REG-SAI.
    43     02 NUM-SAI           PIC 9(05).
    44     02 NOME-SAI          PIC X(20).
    45     02 DD-SAI            PIC 9(02).
    46     02 MM-SAI            PIC 9(02).
    47     02 AAAA-SAI          PIC 9(04).
    48
    49 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    50     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    51
    52 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    53
    54 EXEMPLO.
    55     PERFORM INICIO.
    56     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    57       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:48 Page   2
*                                      EXERC2.CBL
    58     PERFORM TERMINO
    59     STOP RUN.
    60 INICIO.
    61     OPEN INPUT CADALU
    62          OUTPUT CADATU.
    63     PERFORM LEITURA.
    64
    65     LEITURA.
    66         READ CADALU
    67            AT END
    68            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    69 PRINCIPAL.
    70     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    71     PERFORM LEITURA.
    72
    73     GRAVACAO.
    74         MOVE NUM-ENT TO NUM-SAI.
    75         MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-SAI.
    76         MOVE DD-ENT TO DD-SAI.
    77         MOVE MM-ENT TO MM-SAI.
    78         MOVE AAAA-ENT TO AAAA-SAI.
    79         WRITE REG-SAI.
    80
    81 TERMINO.
    82     CLOSE CADALU
    83           CADATU.
